               feloniously<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183209060095"></xptr>forging a receipt for the sum of 1s. 6d., with intent to defraud 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320906-203-victim1694" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Allan
                        <interp inst="t18320906-203-victim1694" type="surname" value="Allan"></interp>
